steps.name: Sort items by visible text: Name (Z to A)

Assertion Is Equal To: Compare Z to A item list with initial item list and check that they are equal - Actual list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)] - Initial list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)]
Sort items by visible text: Price (low to high)

Assertion Is Equal To: Compare Low to High item list with initial item list and check that they are equal - Actual list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)] - Initial list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)]
Sort items by visible text: Price (high to low)

Assertion Is Equal To: Compare High to Low item list with initial item list and check that they are equal - Actual list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)] - Initial list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)]
Sort items by visible text: Name (A to Z)

Assertion Is Equal To: Compare A to Z item list with initial item list and check that they are equal - Actual list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)] - Initial list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)]
